/****************************************************************
replaceDropdown() swaps the dropdown for a Select List to use 
                  HTML elements that can accept styling.
Created by: Mike Behnke
GitHub: https://github.com/localpcguy/ReplaceDropdown
Version: 0.1a
Params: Select ID
Options: "defaults" 
		divIDtext: "LinkList",
		linkIDtext: "Link",
		linkText: "",
		parent: "",
		flipTop: false,
		ddClass: ""
*****************************************************************/